  <brief_title>A Prospective, Multicentre, Open-label Randomised Controlled Study to Investigate the Effectiveness of Pamidronate in the Prevention of Bone Loss in de Novo Renal Transplant Patients.</brief_title>
  <acronym>SMART</acronym>
  <official_title>A 2 Year Prospective, Multicentre, Open-label, Randomised, Controlled Study to Investigate the Effectiveness of Pamidronate in the Prevention of Bone Loss in de Novo Renal Transplant Patients (With a PTH &gt; 150pg/ml) on a Ciclosporin A and Glucocorticoid Based Immunosuppressive Regimen.</official_title>
