  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study was to evaluate the effect of Pamidronate on bone mineral density
      loss and fracture rates up to 2 years, in post renal-transplant subjects on a Ciclosporin A
      and glucocorticoid based immunosuppressive regimen.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
